lass='serviceHeader pb-2'>Get up to R15 000 cash back</div> <p>Get up to R15 000 cash back on your approved home loan amount if you apply online.</p> <p>Visit <span style='text-decoration: underline;'><a style='color: black;' class='e-rte-anchor' href='https://nedbank.co.za/content/nedbank/desktop/gt/en/personal/loans/home-loans.html' title='https://nedbank.co.za/content/nedbank/desktop/gt/en/personal/loans/home-loans.html' target='_blank'>nedbank.co.za/homeloans</a></span></p> <p>* Terms and conditions apply</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pl-1 pr-35px'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>Are you about to settle your home loan?</div> <p>Settling your home loan is a huge financial accomplishment. If you are about to do so, please use the Nedbank Money app or Online Banking (features tab) to request your settlement amount or call us on 0860 555 111.</p> <p>Your account does not automatically close once you have paid up your home loan, you have to follow a bond cancellation process. Your settlement letter has more information, or call us on 0860 555 111.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='row pt-2'> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pr-1'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv250' style='height: 300px;'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>Solar energy finance</div> <p>We understand that the cost of electricity is putting strain on your wallet. We would like to use our money expertise to help you manage your electricity budget. You can finance solar energy solutions with your home loan, which will help you reduce or negate your monthly electricity bill, and you won't have to worry about future electricity tariff hikes. For more information visit <span style='text-decoration: underline;'><a style='color: black;' class='e-rte-anchor' href='https://www.nedbank.co.za/content/nedbank/desktop/gt/en/personal/loans/home-loans/Smart_Living_Solutions.html' title='https://www.nedbank.co.za/content/nedbank/desktop/gt/en/personal/loans/home-loans/Smart_Living_Solutions.html' target='_blank'> Solar Energy Finance </a></span>.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>";

        public const string HOME_LOAN_PRB_NEDBANK_SERVICE_MESSAGE = "<div class='row pt-2'> <div class='col-lg-12'> <div class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left py-0 padding_left_0'> <div class='card-body-header pb-2' style='font-size:12pt !important;'>Nedbank Services</div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='row'> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pr-1'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>Private Clients</div> <p>Our Professional Banking offer has changed to Private Clients. You will still enjoy the same private banking experience packed with exclusive banking, travel and lifestyle benefits. Your dedicated relationship banker is equipped to understand your needs, resolve your queries, manage your credit applications efficiently, give relevant financial advice, or introduce you to a specialist wealth advisor. If you have any questions, contact your dedicated banker. You also have round-the-clock access to our private consultants on 0860 555 222 or at <span style='text-decoration: underline;'><a style='color: black;' class='e-rte-anchor' href='https://nedbank.co.za./' title='https://nedbank.co.za./' target='_blank'>privateclients@nedbank.co.za.</a></span></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pl-1 pr-35px'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>Tax-free investments</div> <p>Make use of your 2022 tax-free allowance from 1 March this year. Take advantage of the compound growth benefits of investing tax-free for yourself, your spouse and your children.</p> <p>We offer tax-free investment solutions in the form of notice period, fixed-term and unit trust accounts.</p> <p>Apply via Online Banking, the Money app or visit https://apply.nedbank.co.za.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='row pt-2'> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pr-1'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>My Cover insurance</div> <p>Our new and exciting MyCover insurance range offers comprehensive cover for you and your family. Choose from homeowner’s (building), household (contents), vehicle and personal-liability cover to create the insurance bundle you need. Or let us help you with a full risk assessment. With our risk consultants working alongside your relationship banker, we offer a seamless experience, from onboarding to handling claims. Contact your dedicated relationship banker or visit private-clients.nedbank.co.za for more information.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pl-1 pr-35px'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>The Essential Guide to Money Management</div> <p>Get a framework with universal financial principles to guide you on the different aspects of managing your money wisely to support your financial well-being. Develop more awareness of the financial choices, opportunities and pitfalls you are likely to be facing at various points during your life. Visit nedbank.co.za/moneymanagement for more information.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='row pt-2'> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pr-1'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv250' style='height: 300px;'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>Money Tracker</div> <p>Track your finances, create budgets and more with MoneyTracker – a free money management tool available on the Nedbank Money app and via Online Banking. Want to track where your money is going? Contact your relationship banker or visit nedbank.co.za/moneytracker for more information.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pl-1 pr-35px'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv250' style='height: 300px;'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>Travel benefits for Private Clients</div> <p>With travel restrictions easing in South Africa and around the world, we would like to remind you of the travel perks you can enjoy with Private Clients offerings. You get unlimited visits to Bidvest airport lounges and automatic basic travel insurance at South African airports for you and secondary cardholders. You also get four airport lounge visits for your children per calendar year and 10 international airport lounge visits to LoungeKey member lounges for you and a guest. Contact your dedicated relationship banker or visit private-clients.nedbank.co.za for more information. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>";

        public const string HOME_LOAN_SBS_NEDBANK_SERVICE_MESSAGE = "<div class='row pt-2'> <div class='col-lg-12'> <div class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left py-0 padding_left_0'> <div class='card-body-header pb-2' style='font-size:12pt !important;'>Nedbank Services</div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='row'> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pr-1'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>SimplyBiz - the free, one-stop platform for business owners when you need it.</div> <p>Get advertising, discounted vouchers, masterclasses, templates, pitch-decks, troubleshooting chats with experts and more - everything your business needs at your fingertips! Join today at simplybiz.co.za.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pl-1 pr-35px'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>Startup Bundle</div> <p>Thinking of starting another business? Then the Startup Bundle is just what you need. Enjoy six months of no monthly fees plus 20 free electronic transactions, a dedicated relationship banker and beyond-banking support. Helping you do big things. Apply now. T&Cs apply </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='row pt-2'> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pr-1'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>Nedbank PocketPOS</div> <p>Our flagship PocketPOS device for small-business owners is a convenient, low-cost solution that you can use in-store and on the go. It’s now available to Nedbank clients for only R89. </p> <p>Contact your relationship banker to apply.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pl-1 pr-35px'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>Nedbank Money Message</div> <p>Join Nedbank Money Message and invite your customers to make quick and secure payments through WhatsApp. Registering as a Money Message merchant is easy – there's no paperwork and no waiting period. Simply add the number for Money Message, +27 (0)87 240 6272, to your contact list and start chatting in WhatsApp by sending 'Hi'. Follow the prompts to complete your registration and start sending invoices to your customers. </p> <p>Visit money-message.co.za to find out more.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='row pt-2'> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pr-1'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv250' style='height: 300px;'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>MoneyTracker</div> <p>Want better control of your cashflow? Track your finances, set budgets, create and manage invoices, and more with MoneyTracker – a free money management tool available on the Money app and Online Banking. Visit nedbank.co.za/moneytracker for more information.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pl-1 pr-35px'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv250' style='height: 300px;'> <div class='serviceHeader pb-2'>Book an appointment with your banker</div> <p>For your convenience, you can now book an appointment with your banker online. Simply log in to the Money app or Online Banking, choose a time slot that suits you and specify whether you prefer to have the meeting over the phone or in person.</p> <p><b> Book your appointment on the Money app: </b>More > Get in touch >Your banker > Book an appointment</p> <p><b> Book your appointment on Online Banking: </b>Get in touch > Book an appointment</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>";

        public const string HOME_LOAN_WEA_NEDBANK_SERVICE_MESSAGE = "<div class='row pt-2'> <div class='col-lg-12'> <div class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left py-0 padding_left_0'> <div class='card-body-header-w pb-2' style='font-size:12pt !important;'>Nedbank Services</div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='row'> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pr-1'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeaderW pb-2'>Home loan fees</div> <p>Our revised pricing schedule applies from 1 January 2022. For more information go to nedbankprivatewealth.co.za.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pl-1 pr-35px'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeaderW pb-2'>eStatements</div> <p>Tired of waiting for the post to arrive? Switch to eStatements today.</p> <p>Visit nedbank.co.za/homeloans or call our service suite to register.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='row pt-2'> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pr-1'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeaderW pb-2'>Nedbank Private Wealth digital tools</div> <p>Try our app and Online Banking. Stay in touch with local and global markets, your wealth and us.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pl-1 pr-35px'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv'> <div class='serviceHeaderW pb-2'>Service Suite</div> <p>The Nedbank Private Wealth Service Suite is available 24/7 for any queries you may have. Call us on 0860 111 263.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='row pt-2'> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pr-1'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv250' style='height: 300px;'> <div class='serviceHeaderW pb-2'>Social Media</div> <p>You can now follow Nedbank Private Wealth on LinkedIn, Facebook and Twitter.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class='col-lg-6 col-md-6 pl-1 pr-35px'> <div id='{{WidgetId}}' class='card border-0'> <div class='card-body text-left p-0'> <div class='ServicesDiv250' style='height: 300px;'> <div class='serviceHeaderW pb-2'>Are you about to settle your home loan?</div> <p>Settling your home loan is a huge financial accomplishment. If you are about to do so, please use the Nedbank Private Wealth app or Online Banking (features tab) to request your settlement amount or call us on 0860 111 263.</p> <p> Your account does not automatically close once you have paid up your home loan - you have to follow a bond cancellation process.Your settlement letter has more information, or call us on 0860 111 263 </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>";

